The paper deals with an end-to-end machine-human image annotation system, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) for feature extraction, machine learning (cs.AI) for classification, human-computer interaction (cs.HC) for task sampling, and crowd sourcing (cs.LG, cs.IR) for consensus. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
